(39520, 'zhCN', 'Ashran Dominance', 'Defeat the Alliance at the event locations in Ashran and kill Grand Marshal Tremblade.', 'The Alliance refuse to back down in Ashran. Teach them that the Horde will not stand aside while they plunder the power of the ancient ogre empire to use for their own schemes.', '', 'Grand Marshal Tremblade leads the Alliance forces in Ashran.', 'Grand Marshal Tremblade', '', '', '', 33528),
